    "description": "这款VR专属动作射击游戏让旧西部变得栩栩如生！《黑色足迹》将把你带进一个充满激情的战争故事里，体验极佳的旧西部动作情境。<br><br>故事发生在淘金热时代，就在白人发现遗物的几天后，土著人袭击了蛇谷矿区。杰克是一名老赏金猎人，而白鹰是一名受人尊敬的战士，他们都出于不同的原因在寻找两件遗物。<br><br>在一个个章节中，玩家在杰克和白鹰之间切换，使用有历史代表性的独特武器，在狂野的旧西部世界与上百人战斗，改变战争的命运。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/8accce285e2d37ee5a38b28d13f1c937.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/8accce285e2d37ee5a38b28d13f1c937.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/8accce285e2d37ee5a38b28d13f1c937.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>不断变化的游戏内容</strong><br>《黑色足迹》因其独特的章节设计而提供非重复性的游戏体验。在每个章节中，你会在杰克和白鹰之间切换，装备一套新的武器，和不同的敌人战斗，同时探索新环境。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/251d11c7121d7cad42b8b6e52c7bb153.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/251d11c7121d7cad42b8b6e52c7bb153.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/251d11c7121d7cad42b8b6e52c7bb153.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>独特的武器物品组合</strong><br>在《黑色足迹》的每一章中，你都将获得一个新的武器物品组合和一个新的任务。每种武器都有其独特的互动风格，这将把每个章节转变为新的独特的战斗体验。你会得心应手地使用你的新武器。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/cb17686d6adda2b34659bf437277958c.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/cb17686d6adda2b34659bf437277958c.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/cb17686d6adda2b34659bf437277958c.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>双线叙事风格</strong><br>每个故事都有两面。《黑色足迹》的故事是通过杰克和白鹰的视角，在各个章节之间配有完整叙述的动画短片来讲述的。杰克是一个无忧无虑的老赏金猎人，而白鹰是一个怒不可遏、复仇心切的部落领袖。他们在与彼此、时间和数百个敌人战斗的过程中，试图拿到新发现的古老遗物。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/109c1d8022fbc649888ed403a7d6ff10.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/109c1d8022fbc649888ed403a7d6ff10.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/109c1d8022fbc649888ed403a7d6ff10.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>仿真的机器机关</strong><br>给步枪上膛，投掷斧子，用盾牌挡子弹，给左轮手枪上弹，抽出弓箭，转动加特林枪的手柄……武器和物品的设计都尽可能接近现实生活，为了提供流畅的VR体验。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/d0add72856eb8d1ddbcb82720b960ed0.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/d0add72856eb8d1ddbcb82720b960ed0.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/d0add72856eb8d1ddbcb82720b960ed0.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>多种移动设置</strong><br>在虚拟现实中探索广阔的西部世界，同时能够对抗数百个敌人，这要求非常自然的移动。在《黑色足迹》中，移动方式不局限于一种，你将能够随时行走和瞬移。当你战斗、隐蔽或寻找弹药时，体验逼真的机动性，同时最大限度地减少眩晕的影响。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/122557c71ee6c2186fe13023bd2214e2.poster.avif?t=1713267722\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/122557c71ee6c2186fe13023bd2214e2.webm?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576420/extras/122557c71ee6c2186fe13023bd2214e2.mp4?t=1713267722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>灵感源自旧西部的环境和仿佛身临其境的画面</strong><br>解放被占领的西部城镇，在行进的军用火车中战斗，走进金矿深处……精心设计的旧西部风格的环境，沉浸式的画面，以及虚拟现实的加持，都会让你成为这个时代的一部分。",
